archimate:DataObject.name: Entity
archimate:DataObject.documentation: As used in IETF RFC 3986, Uniform Resource Identifier (URI), a resource of any kind that can be uniquely and independently identified. An Entity identified by a Sovrin DID is a Sovrin Entity. See also Identity.
